body.content:
Hello handsome,

I'm taken already but are you ready for a special gift?

I am headed out to TX this weekend to join my soul mate, I will 
be shutting down my account in honor of my partner.

I am online now and was about to shut down my account - as I 
already got a life partner here on my dating site but my cousin 
Catherine believes in the same chance meeting, she saw your 
profile as I was surfing through profiles and viewing pages, she 
was actually standing behind me watching over my shoulder and I 
was showing her the ropes and how it works on dating sites. She 
was awe struck when your profile popped up, I never knew any 
peace of mind from that very moment, she has been all over me 
about getting in touch with you.

She said you seem like a man she will like to know better. She 
lives in the same area as you. she was only here for a job 
inspection. You don't need to write back here as I will be 
deactivating my account on this site soonest. This is her direct 
email: cathydkuhns@aliyun.com

Be a gentleman and reach out to her, I assure you Catherine is a 
fun and open-minded lovable personality,  a true woman of 
substance seeking a long term relationship.

I'm confident that you will thank me later for this blind date.

All the best.

Shirley K
